  "subject": "CI: Update CBOM workflow with fixes",
  "commit_message": "CI: Update CBOM workflow with fixes\n\nReplace unconditional checkout-gerrit-change-action with\nconditional logic for three event scenarios:\n- push: 10s replication delay then actions/checkout\n- workflow_dispatch with Gerrit: checkout-gerrit-change\n- workflow_dispatch with GERRIT_DISABLED: actions/checkout\n\nAdd the missing gerrit-project input and update all\npinned action versions to their latest releases.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I9e4061d58488ff74ee064c0219a53fa8285b745b\nCo-authored-by: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
